1.5 to 3 T Electric Bravo Series

  • Home
  • Product
  • 1.5 to 3 T Electric Bravo Series

Features :

1.5 to 3 tonne capacity at 500 mm load center; lift heights up to 7.2 m

2-stage / 2-stage with full free lift / 3-stage with full free lift , Container stuffing and destuffing made easy with container mast(optional)

Twin motor technology offers excellent performance like diesel truck with 21 % gradebility & 15 Kmph speed.

Electronic differential and unique steering axle offer class leading turning radius of 1.77 m/ 1.98 m.

Energy efficient, maintenance free AC technology for traction and hydraulics enhances energy saving, battery life and handling performance
